## Wallet 3: attacker initialization and drain
Wallet 3 proxy: 0xCf7Ed3AccA5a467e9e704C703E8D87F634fB0Fc9
Wallet 3 balance before exploit: 5.0 ETH
Attacker is owner before initWallet: false
Attacker is owner after unauthorized initWallet: true
